Nonfried at ZMHB (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 57" captionStartId="F57" captionText="Figure 57. Pelidnota tricolor Nonfried (valid name Pelidnota burmeisteri tricolor Nonfried) syntype male from ZMHB. A Dorsal habitus B Lateral habitus C Male genitalia, lateral view D Male parameres, caudal view E Specimen labels." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.666.9191.figure57" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/130485" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">57</figureCitation>
). 1 ♂ holotype of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ohaus" authorityYear="1905" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Pelidnota" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pelidnota ludovici" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ludovici">
